### Notes:
# 1. Replace {{token}} with a valid JWT token for a candidate user
# 2. For resume upload, you need an actual PDF file in the same directory
# 3. This API ONLY extracts data - it does NOT create any database records
# 4. All extracted data will be displayed in the console
# 5. The response contains the extracted data ready for form population
# 6. File must be PDF format and under 10MB
# 7. Check your server console for detailed extraction logs

### Expected Response Structure:
# The API will return:
# - success: true/false
# - message: Description of the operation
# - data.extracted_data: Complete extracted CV data
# - data.file_info: Information about the uploaded file
# - data.extraction_summary: Count of extracted items by category

### Console Output:
# The API will log detailed information to the console including:
# - Basic information (name, title, contact details)
# - Work experience details
# - Education information
# - Skills and proficiency levels
# - Projects and technologies
# - Certificates and awards
# - Volunteering experience
# - Language proficiencies
# - Accomplishments
